Map between individual Clarkson's Vessel_Type and generalizable ship types used in IMO GHG 3 (imoShipType) and Starcrest (starcrestShipType) inventories.

shipMap.Rd

Map between individual Clarkson's Vessel_Type and generalizable ship types used in IMO GHG 3 (imoShipType) and Starcrest (starcrestShipType) inventories.

data(shipMap)

Format

A data frame with 341 rows and 3 variables:

Vessel_Type

Specific Clarkson's Vessel_Type.

imoShipType

Generalizable ship types alligning with IMO GHG 3 auxiliary and boiler loads.

starcrestShipType

Generalizable ship types alligning with starcrest 2016 auxiliary and boiler loads.

Details

This is used in calcShipType.r

References

International Maritime Organization.Third IMO GHG Study 2014 - Final Report. London: International Maritime Organization, 2014. Starcrest Consulting Group,LLC.Port of Los Angeles Inventory of Air Emissions-2016, 2017.

Examples

data(shipMap)
